{"tid":893884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想表白嘅你麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2018-11-08T03:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T04:40:12.000Z","uid":201931,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b63b347397a1dc3e8fec45d07ee0a6a4aba2653a","tid":893884,"uid":201931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:44:04.000Z","msg":"呢排有個男仔向我表白 但明明我同佢只係識左兩個月仲要唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對話次數少於十次 冇單獨相處過/傾過計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我被表白後完全係黑人問號 我哪來的吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以有感而發要寫呢個po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一 你完全未認識我 點解可以咁快同我講你好鐘意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你連我住邊區 甚至我中文名點寫你都未必知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐘意一個人應該係要相處落先知 而唔係憑外表/覺得人地幾挽得就想追人 呢啲極其量只係好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就算比你地一齊到 都好難長久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 膚淺啲諗 至少都要知道對方有咩興趣先可以r話題架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果呢項都未做到就去表白嗰啲 一係就player一係就on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二 表白係比對方知你嘅心意 結果唔係一齊就係食檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失敗左你可能會想繼續追佢 但係其實你咁chur對方只會對你反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知男仔點諗 但一般女仔都好怕男仔成日打電話黎搵你/成日想約你食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知道你好想將對方追到手 但係就算唔係拖都要有冷靜期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔怕面懵對方都怕尷尬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冷靜一陣 諗清楚 真係鐘意既再行動都未遲#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千其唔好將對方嗰小小好感變埋反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過真心問 遲啲上堂見到好尷尬點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後 祝準備表白嘅你成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea590eebed75217de7697ea5321e6b9b91e5d474","tid":893884,"uid":157487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"識佐成兩個月仲唔夠？"},{"pid":"30ce3b4880514cd809a74ca431de90d0ee74f5e5","tid":893884,"uid":157487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"你無feel姐"},{"pid":"3e2a90a8030258c51b06127f28425b5f2e250f94","tid":893884,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:02:54.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"87f0cd0d493ce9d3f7c7ef5d987442a0dd53d74b","tid":893884,"uid":218766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea590eebed75217de7697ea5321e6b9b91e5d474","tid":893884,"uid":157487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"識佐成兩個月仲唔夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"對話次數少於<span style=\"color: red;\">十</span>次 <span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>單獨相處過/傾過計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103e59ffb61797595bbb09a4b8abd9d23b184e07","tid":893884,"uid":201931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87f0cd0d493ce9d3f7c7ef5d987442a0dd53d74b","tid":893884,"uid":218766,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea590eebed75217de7697ea5321e6b9b91e5d474","tid":893884,"uid":157487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"識佐成兩個月仲唔夠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"對話次數少於<span style=\"color: red;\">十</span>次 <span style=\"color: red;\">冇</span>單獨相處過/傾過計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d38787db7065a